pinal Labyrinth》是他们一月份发行的上一张单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lennon-gallaghers-automotion-share-faris-badawan-produced-new-single-liquify-3577808">《Liquify》</a>的后续作品。这首歌由乐队与 Faris Badwan（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/artists/the-horrors">The Horrors</a>的主唱）合作制作。</p><p> Automotion 于 2021 年分享了他们的首张 EP <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lennon-gallaghers-band-automotion-release-debut-ep-today-2957779">《In Motion》</a> ，乐队将其描述为“技术在社会中的主导地位、成为和克服以及创造新事物的旅程的开始”。</p><p>该系列之后是 EP <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lennon-gallaghers-automotion-announce-new-ep-ecstatic-oscillations-3263055">“Ecstatic Oscillations”</a> （2022 年）和“Artificial Ascent”（2023 年）。 </p><figure id="attachment_3577815" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3577815" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3577815" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Automotion@2000x1270.jpg" alt="汽车，2024" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Automotion@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Automotion@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Automotion@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Automotion@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Automotion@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Automotion@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3577815" class="wp-caption-text"> Automotion，2024。来源：@caty_magenta</figcaption></figure><p>利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/liam-gallagher-cover-interview-2022-cmon-you-know-3163407">) 在 2022 年接受<em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">NME</em></a