100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3466104" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：Arturo Holmes/MG23/Getty Images for The Met Museum/Vogue</figcaption></figure><p>原版电影改编自艾德·麦克贝恩的小说《<em>国王的赎金</em>》，三船敏郎饰演一名富翁，被迫为雇员被绑架的儿子支付赎金。</p><p> <em>《High And Low》</em>的翻拍版将由 A24 在电影院上映，然后在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/apple-tv">Apple TV+</a>上上映（据<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/film/2024/feb/08/spike-lee-denzel-washington-akira-kurosawa-movie-remake" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a>报道），不过电影上映和流媒体的上映日期尚未公布。</p><p>斯派克·李的《 <em>High And Low》</em>版本将标志着他与丹泽尔·华盛顿的第五次合作。他们过去的合作作品包括 1990 年的<em>Mo&#39; Better Blues</em> 、1992 年的<em>Malcom X</em> 、1998 年的<em>He Got Game</em>和 2006 年的<em>Inside Man</em> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3585093" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3585093" style="width: 1476px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3585093" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington.jpg" alt="" width="1476" height="1014" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington.jpg 1476w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-218x150.jpg 218w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-436x300.jpg 436w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-400x275.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-800x550.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-696x478.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-1392x956.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Spike-Lee-and-Denzel-Washington-1068x734.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1476px) 100vw, 1476px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3585093" class="wp-caption-text">斯派克·李和丹泽尔·华盛顿。图片来源：盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>在 Ice Spice 方面，这位说唱歌手将于今年某个时候发行她备受期待的首张专辑《Y2K》。据说唱歌手称，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ice-spice-confirms-y2k-album-is-finished-3597276">这张专辑“已经完成”</a> ，并且<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ice-spice-has-been-playing-album-at-full-volume-to-pass-the-car-test-3614999">最近“通过了汽车测试”</a> 。</p><p> 《Y2K》将接续这位布朗克斯说唱歌手 2023 年 1 月的 EP <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/ice-spice-like-debut-project-review-bikini-bottom-radar-3383027#:~:text=Much%20like%20the%20sardonic%20vocals,project%2C%20such%20a%20sharp%20listen.">《Like..?》</a> ，其中包括《Munch (Feelin&#39; U)》和《In Ha Mood》等热门歌曲。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/ice-spice-like-debut-project-review-bikini-bottom-radar-3383027#:~:text=Much%20like%20the%20sardonic%20vocals,project%2C%20such%20a%20sharp%20listen."><em>NME</em>授予该版本四颗星</a>，Thomas Smith 称赞 Ice Spice 的讽刺风格和冷静的自信。</p><p> “对于 Ice Spice 来说，路还很长，度过病毒爆发后的时期感觉至关重要：长寿感觉是可以实现的，但临时听众甚至一些粉丝仍然善变，”史密斯写道。 “在‘​​喜欢……？’节目中，她似乎并不在意追逐影响力或粉丝——她知道无论如何他们最终都会回心转意。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/ice-spice-to-star-alongside-denzel-washington-in-new-spike-lee-film-3616289">冰辣妹 (Ice Spice) 与丹泽尔·华盛顿 (Denzel Washington) 共同主演斯派克·李 (Spike Lee) 的新</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">电影</a></p>;
向去世的纽约传奇 DJ Mister Cee 致敬https://www.nme.com/news/music/tributes-paid-to-legendary-new-york-dj-mister-cee-who-has-died-3616259?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=tributes-paid-致已去世的纽约传奇 DJ 西伊先生Surej SinghThu, 11 Apr 2024 03:20:16 +0000 Music NewsNews..Rap https://www.nme.com/?p=3616259 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mister-cee@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mister-cee@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mister-cee@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mister-cee@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mister-cee@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mister-cee@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mister-cee@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Cee 先生帮助录制了 The Notorious BIG 的首张演示磁带，并担任其首张专辑的执行制作人</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tributes-paid-to-legendary-new-york-dj-mister-cee-who-has-died-3616259">向去世的纽约传奇 DJ Mister Cee 致敬的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mister-cee@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mister-cee@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mister-cee@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mister-cee@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mister-cee@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mister-cee@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/mister-cee@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>来自纽约市的传奇 DJ Mister Cee 去世，享年 57 岁。</p><p> Cee（真名 Calvin LeBrun）是纽约 Hot 97 广播电台的长期 DJ。Hot 97 宣布了他的去世，并<a href="https://www.hot97.com/news/legendary-dj-mister-cee-has-passed-away/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在他们的网站上写道</a>：“作为 HOY 97 和 WBLS 的一家人，我们对他的去世深感悲痛。”我们敬爱的西先生去世了。他不仅仅是一名 DJ；他是我们电台的支柱，他在《Noon》和《Friday Night Live》中传奇般的复古风格为无数听众带来欢乐。”</p><p> HOT 97 继续说道： Cee 的影响力远远超出了广播领域，塑造了纽约 DJ 文化的本质。当我们向他的家人和他的音乐所影响的歌迷致以我们的爱和慰问时，我们的心情十分沉重。安息吧，Cee 先生，您的遗产将永远存在。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5mCUv4pWIH/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852